HEADWORD: Nervure
<hw>Nerv"ure</hw> <pr>(n⟦etil⟧rv"⟦usl⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
See <er>Nerve</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>One of the
nerves of leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of the chitinous supports, or
veins, in the wings of insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nervus</ent>⟦br⟧
